WEBVTT

1
00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:23.120
Did you know that all time your patients can even forget the taste of their spouses?

2
00:00:23.120 --> 00:00:27.539
But they never forget the smell of these flowers.

3
00:00:27.539 --> 00:00:32.689
You should taste the smell before, of course.

4
00:00:32.689 --> 00:00:40.590
Purple lotus. I love them.

5
00:00:40.590 --> 00:00:41.590
There you go.

6
00:00:41.590 --> 00:00:52.500
What are you doing with these flowers?

7
00:00:52.500 --> 00:00:58.170
Let's say, I'm trying to remind people of myself.

8
00:00:58.170 --> 00:01:10.120
Sorry, I can't.

9
00:01:10.120 --> 00:01:13.310
There's something more important I shouldn't forget.

10
00:01:13.310 --> 00:01:14.310
What's that?

11
00:01:14.310 --> 00:01:17.879
My allergy of flowers.

